name: EntrepreneurFinder.com
tag_list: jobs, entrepreneurship, networking, investors, professionals, students, startup
overview:
EntrepreneurFinder.com is a free interactive resource designed around the needs of entrepreneurs, professionals, students and investors.

EF is designed for those looking to:

Form new industry contacts. Find a mentor or mentor others. Find great companies in need of funding. Search for the right investors and raise capital for a startup or an existing business. Find employment, freelance and internship opportunities. Find the right business partner, employee, freelancer or intern. Access an extensive directory of local and international trade shows and conferences. Stay current with news, information and other business resources.

The site covers everything from students looking for mentors to recruiters and entrepreneurs looking for professionals to investors looking for the next great company in search of funding. Entrepreneur Finder brings all these groups together to find employment, grow their company or to form new industry contacts for a reason. The site is about creating free tools that help users throughout their professional or entrepreneurial careers.
